d":27936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T21:08:26.000Z","msg":"好好睇！！！支持"},{"pid":"e863837e339f1e79c68b5c310ee50783947a0fd5","tid":2463486,"uid":79789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"010ca5e257ed810878faf308a7434e29cbad06bf","tid":2463486,"uid":17786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T20:37:46.000Z","msg":"99% sad end<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T21:16:24.000Z","msg":"我知1%就係到出現 如果唔係我斬死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4317510a37afe9d898616139d1d2ead67b353b","tid":2463486,"uid":337336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T22:06:36.000Z","msg":"接受她的愛吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635ac5ddc34e97b0698cb97a5e8cdcaee0f4c15e","tid":2463486,"uid":138590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T22:18:44.000Z","msg":"正 樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a65d4170c81dcffd94f6cc758d7088277982bf9","tid":2463486,"uid":32672,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T23:09:33.000Z","msg":"夠50正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在諾士佛臺淺酌有一個好處，就算喝得微醺，走回尖東香格里拉也算不上太遠。<br />\n<br />\n我們點了一支白酒，酒保端了兩隻玻璃杯過來，然後把替我們倒酒，酒保離去後，家瑜一臉陶醉的跟我說：<br />\n<br />\n「你仲記唔記得呀？」<br />\n<br />\n我心領神會她所指的：<br />\n<br />\n「五個月前嘅情人節你嚟揾我，仲飲咗杯醉生夢死嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n「算你啦，仲記得！不過我哋都唔係喺呢間吧度飲。」<br />\n<br />\n「無計啦，返酒店遠嘛，而且我而家都唔需要飲醉生夢死呀。」<br />\n<br />\n她捉著我的手問道：<br />\n<br />\n「係咩？」<br />\n<br />\n「係呀。」<br />\n<br />\n看著她用著優雅的姿態端著酒杯，淺淺的喝上一口，也是一件賞心悅目的事。<br />\n<br />\n我們一邊端祥著對方，一邊喝著酒，慢慢地連酒也喝了半支，正所謂酒不醉人自醉，這刻連心也醉了。<br />\n<br />\n突然酒吧來了一隊樂隊，他們開始演唱了一首絕對符合我們心情的歌曲，是Ed Sheeran  - Perfect。<br />\n<br />\n看來我們選對了酒吧，這間酒吧過了某個時段便有一個位置供人起舞，樂隊唱著這首歌的時候，已經有三對情侶，在舞池與另一半起舞，雖然三對入面有兩對是外藉人士，有一對是老夫老妻。<br />\n<br />\n也許，酒精令人壯膽，我的眼神稍為看了舞池，家瑜笑著並尷尬的搖了搖頭，我走到她身旁，裝作傳統舞會邀請舞伴的牽起她的手，剛好其中一對外藉情侶見狀走了過來，女的輕輕請了家瑜跟隨著我的步伐來到舞池；<br />\n<br />\n在舞池裡，雖然我們沒有如其他情侶般起舞，只是她緊緊的摟著我的腰間，我也擁著她，跟隨著歌曲的旋律輕擺著我們的身子。<br />\n<br />\n然後，我輕吻她的額頭，她主動的吻著我的臉頰，我把頭向下傾著，靠近那張暖和的櫻桃小嘴，緩和的隨歌曲的節奏吻著，而我們就這樣旁若無人般的在舞池熱吻，其他人彷彿就像為我們而起舞作伴，我深信我們的腦海在那個瞬間，同樣幻想著花瓣漫天飛舞，我不知道這首歌曲貼合過多少愛侶的心情，這個地方也造就過甚麼故事，只知道一首四分鐘的歌曲，但對我們而言時間猶如被凝住了，今晚是如此完美，眼前的她也是完美，當下的四分鐘也如歌曲名一樣，是Perfect。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RWd7NoYfmxk&amp;ab_channel=%E8%A5%BF%E6%B4%8BMusic%E3%80%89Wisher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRWd7NoYfmxk%26ab_channel%3D%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%25B4%258BMusic%25E3%2580%2589Wisher&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWnG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=d6d5e75e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RWd7NoYfmxk&amp;ab_channel=%E8%A5%BF%E6%B4%8BMusic%E3%80%89Wisher</a><br />\n<br />\n待續<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426a0f1fc343e09e22185678f690a8ce1f1d51f9","tid":2463486,"uid":154478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T23:24:55.000Z","msg":"在線上"},{"pid":"f75b6bb30910dbf0b9b00a5564c763871d00a524","tid":2463486,"uid":395157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T23:42:31.000Z","msg":"支持，感謝"},{"pid":"08592628ac9a36e8999e052a8cca71348ee5f03c","tid":2463486,"uid":354890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T23:50:06.000Z","msg":"在線上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27763e2f09173e5b86a919b1510bacc1d8232b2","tid":2463486,"uid":285154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T23:54:19.000Z","msg":"好多文<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d253948d76ff68b0c48f6bd87eef1427e244df2","tid":2463486,"uid":17786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e863837e339f1e79c68b5c310ee50783947a0fd5","tid":2463486,"uid":79789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"010ca5e257ed810878faf308a7434e29cbad06bf","tid":2463486,"uid":17786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T20:37:46.000Z","msg":"99% sad end<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T21:16:24.000Z","msg":"我知1%就係到出現 如果唔係我斬死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:00:28.000Z","msg":"希望啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595bea5942784f982ab242872284822e392dc841","tid":2463486,"uid":154847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:12:48.000Z","msg":"繼續"},{"pid":"6610ff4f3b7a65b9f9f8b96c8ae6a94c455fbaaa","tid":2463486,"uid":128065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T00:27:34.000Z","msg":"留名在線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />